n) In the context of the Rashtrasant Tukadoji Maharaj Shetkari Bhawan Scheme. The terms and conditions in the original Government Decision of 19.12.2023 shall continue to apply.

r) Technical Sanction should be provided to the budget for the construction of this Kisan Bhawan by the Deputy Engineer (Construction), Public Works Department working in the Marketing Directorate. Only after this, the tender process should be carried out as per the prescribed procedure and the commencement orders should be issued.
The Secretary of the market committee concerned should submit the progress report of this construction to the District Sub-Registrar, Cooperative Society, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar from time to time.
The construction of Kisan Bhawan should be completed within one year from the date of administrative sanction.
